(262, 1, '2017-02-21 14:01:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Hurra, unser 3-jähriger Hengst von Diarado x Grundyman xx hat jetzt auch den 50-Tage-Test bestanden und darf nächstes Jahr decken!!! Jetzt muss ich mich nur bald für einen Namen entscheiden! Ganz vielen Dank an das Team in Adelheidsdorf für die tolle Arbeit!!!\\nUnseren 4-jährigen Chacco\'s Crack haben wir jetzt auch wieder bei uns nach erfolgreicher TG Produktion durch Detlef Utecht van Dijk. Ab jetzt wird geritten und sich ganz auf den Sport konzentriert!', '50-Tage-Test', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-21 14:01:27', '2017-02-21 14:01:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/fso_eventing/?p=262', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(264, 1, '2017-02-21 14:31:03', '2017-02-21 14:31:03', '[vc_row][vc_column el_class=\"fso-animation\"][vc_column_text]\\n<h2>About Ostholt Eventing</h2>\\nSara Algotsson Ostholt, swedish eventing rider with long time experince of horses and a silver medal from the Olympics 2012 in London with her horse Wega. Together with Frank Ostholt, german eventing rider with a gold medal from Olympics 2008 in Peking are the head of Ostholt Eventing. Placed in the town of horses Warendorf, Germany.\\n\\nHere at Ostholt Eventing is it all about the horses. We are breeding for the future, training our horses to reach the top, and nearly every weekend off to eventing competitions with both young and experienced horses. We have also horses for sale, so are you looking for a young horse, experienced horse, show jumping horse, eventing horse or what ever you\'re searching for don\'t hesitate to contact us! Or check out our horses here![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'START', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-02-21 14:31:03', '2017-02-21 14:31:03', '', 60, 'http://localhost:8888/fso_eventing/2017/02/21/60-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2017-02-21 14:33:03', '2017-02-21 14:33:03', '[vc_row][vc_column el_class=\"fso-animation\"][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h2>About Ostholt Eventing</h2>\\r\\nSara Algotsson Ostholt, swedish eventing rider with long time experince of horses and a silver medal from the Olympics 2012 in London with her horse Wega. Together with Frank Ostholt, german eventing rider with a gold medal from Olympics 2008 in Peking are the head of Ostholt Eventing. Placed in the town of horses Warendorf, Germany.\\r\\n\\r\\nHere at Ostholt Eventing is it all about the horses. We are breeding for the future, training our horses to reach the top, and nearly every weekend off to eventing competitions with both young and experienced horses. We have also horses for sale, so are you looking for a young horse, experienced horse, show jumping horse, eventing horse or what ever you\'re searching for don\'t hesitate to contact us! Or check out our horses here![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'START', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-21 14:33:03', '2017-02-21 14:33:03', '', 60, 'http://localhost:8888/fso_eventing/2017/02/21/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(266, 1, '2017-02-21 14:53:20', '2017-02-21 14:53:20', '[vc_row][vc_column el_class=\"fso-animation\"][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h2>Om Ostholt Eventing</h2>\\r\\nSara Algotsson Ostholt, svensk fälttävlansryttare med lång erfarenhet av hästar och en silver medalj fran OS i London 2012 med hästen Wega. Tillsammans med Frank Ostholt, tysk fälttävlansryttere, även han mycket erfaren och en guld medalj från OS i Peking är de spetsen av Ostholt Eventing. Placerade i Warendorf, Tyskland.\\r\\n\\r\\nHär på Ostholt Eventing handlar allt om hästar. Vi föder upp hästar för framtiden, tränar våra hästar med sikte mot toppen, och nästintill varenda helg åker vi på tävling med bade våra unga och mer rutinerade hästar.  Vi har även hästar till salu, sa söker du efter en unghäst, rutinerad häst, hopphäst eller fälttävlanshäst, tveka inte att höra av dig till oss! Eller kolla på våra hästar här![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'START', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '143-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-21 14:53:20', '2017-02-21 14:53:20', '', 143, 'http://localhost:8888/fso_eventing/2017/02/21/143-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
